		<h4>Early Vertebrate Fossil Identification and Anatomy – what does it tell us about our own evolution?</h4>
		<p><strong>Date:</strong> Sunday, March 15, 2026</p>
		<p><strong>Location:</strong> Room B140, Main Building Level 1 (lower level), Mount Royal University</p>
